            "answer_text": "By normal I assume IPS LCD Simple thing is These are two different technologies Super AMOLED has better colors and inky blacks when compared to LCD, but its also expensive, HD+ OLED(720p+) would be better for content consumption (videos, photos) on screen sizes less than 6.3 inches, for bigger screens and main use is reading text, I'd recommend FHD+ LCD(1080p+) ",
